title: 'Decomposed body’ found in Victorian national park - 9news.com.au
text:
'Decomposed body’ found in Victorian national park By 9NEWS 
A woman’s decomposed body has reportedly been found at a national park in Macedon, north-west of Melbourne. 
Police have set up a crime scene at Macedon Regional Park, the Bendigo Advertiser reports. 
The body is “considerably decomposed”, according to the newspaper. This is a breaking news story. More detail will be added shortly. Get breaking news alerts when a major story happens near you by downloading the 9NEWS Alerts app, available on iPhone and Android. © Nine Digital Pty Ltd 2017
